modifier.attuned.name=Attuned
modifier.attuned.desc=§oIn sync with the world!§r\nRepairing gives bonus durability based on vis and flux in the Aura.

modifier.aural.name=Aural
modifier.aural.desc=§oIt all bounces back, right?§r\nTool use has a chance of feeding off of the Aura instead of using durability

modifier.brilliance.name=Brilliance
modifier.brilliance.desc=§oShine!§r\nEnemies that hit you glow and receive night vision.

modifier.corrosive.name=Corrosive
modifier.corrosive.desc=§oEdgy!§r\nMaterial corrodes over time in The Betweenlands. Does 35% bonus damage to mobs from that dimension. Repair to clear corrosion.
